{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"efcc5203ef","title":"大字报诗——致谭天荣","origin":"北京大学社会主义思想教育委员会编印《北京大学右派分子反动言论汇集》，一九五七年十月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d4244359be","index":0,"year":1957,"month":7,"day":null,"articleId":"efcc5203ef"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"b1a23c6fa5","name":"杨路"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3c052d698a","type":"title","text":"大字报诗——致谭天荣","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"efcc5203ef"},{"id":"997955cebb","type":"authors","text":"北京大学杨路","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"efcc5203ef"},{"id":"edee6cb6c1","type":"subtitle","text":"（谭天荣：北京大学物理系学生；杨路：北京大学数学系学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"efcc5203ef"},{"id":"1d1a824732","type":"paragraph","text":"你还记得吗？","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"efcc5203ef"},{"id":"258e7f143a","type":"paragraph","text":"契柯夫的话：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"efcc5203ef"},{"id":"3e9d60d02d","type":"paragraph","text":"越是高尚就越是不幸，","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"efcc5203ef"},{"id":"d08208ef83","type":"paragraph","text":"庸碌的人容易得到满足，","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"efcc5203ef"},{"id":"86a7eae816","type":"paragraph","text":"因为他们不懂得永生。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"efcc5203ef"},{"id":"0e55e74115","type":"paragraph","text":"拜伦也曾破过偶象。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"efcc5203ef"},{"id":"7c836514f9","type":"paragraph","text":"阿！伟大的精灵。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"efcc5203ef"},{"id":"1742f3e177","type":"appellation","text":"……","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"efcc5203ef"},{"id":"c49e28f439","type":"paragraph","text":"我与你志气同在，谭天荣。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"efcc5203ef"},{"id":"8125c00e1a","type":"paragraph","text":"如果你还眷恋着这冷漠的人群。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"efcc5203ef"},{"id":"4fe4df3750","type":"paragraph","text":"如果你还居然保存着信心，","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"efcc5203ef"},{"id":"759e47102a","type":"paragraph","text":"那你就战斗吧！","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"efcc5203ef"},{"id":"5374acb1e7","type":"paragraph","text":"啊！希望属于未来，希望属于黎明！","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"efcc5203ef"}],"page":{"id":"48daadcb7e","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"efcc5203ef","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}